{"tid":1143053,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"俄媒：華為可能獲俄羅斯超3.8億美元存儲系統合同","createTime":"2019-05-07T12:58:12.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-07T13:49:28.000Z","uid":228346,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"3a460cd65d6fc79d7b7f68c3664ad4054cfa90d4","tid":1143053,"uid":228346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-07T12:58:12.000Z","msg":"據俄羅斯衛星通訊社報道，有三位知情人士向媒體透露，華為或將獲得價值 3.837 億美元（250 億盧布）的合同，為俄羅斯數據存儲系統提供設備。<br />\n<br />\n2016 年，俄羅斯總統簽署的反恐法要求，電信運營商和互聯網公司需存儲用戶的有關信息，並在情報部門要求時加以提供。信息包括用戶的談話和通信內容，以及照片、視頻和聲音文件。<br />\n<br />\n此前有俄媒報道，Norsi-Trans 公司為電信公司 MTS 及其子公司 MGTS 從事法律的技術落實工作。前者在測試後選擇了華為設備。為此，MTS 將把 500 億盧布（約合 7.675 億美元）中的近半費用花在這些設備上。"},{"pid":"385258682c8a275149d3d6d9ac4d1af810ad14eb","tid":1143053,"uid":53026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-05-07T13:01:40.000Z","msg":"大佬都搞？"},{"pid":"71e79501ebb639583cb5bd3eff89b5f9fc1ced18","tid":1143053,"uid":44171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-07T13:02:09.000Z","msg":"俄佬仲有美元找數？"},{"pid":"0cb291c7f86226ab88517ef3d65899e6ddd45df5","tid":1143053,"uid":68097,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"71e79501ebb639583cb5bd3eff89b5f9fc1ced18","tid":1143053,"uid":44171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-07T13:02:09.000Z","msg":"俄佬仲有美元找數？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-07T13:05:11.000Z","msg":"以盧布支付 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e987c305e80824b92347e2732787806ea809118a","tid":1143053,"uid":36724,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0cb291c7f86226ab88517ef3d65899e6ddd45df5","tid":1143053,"uid":68097,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"71e79501ebb639583cb5bd3eff89b5f9fc1ced18","tid":1143053,"uid":44171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-07T13:02:09.000Z","msg":"俄佬仲有美元找數？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-07T13:05:11.000Z","msg":"以盧布支付 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"re